Market Analysis and Insights:

Global Spring Water Market

The spring watermarked size is expected to reach a value of USD 97,862.39 million by 2028. Spring watermarked report analyses the growth, which is currently being growing due to the rapid change in the water consumption habits.

The spring water generally contains a variety of minerals such as magnesium, sodium and calcium. But the amount of minerals varies based on the source from which this spring water is bottled.

The increase in per capita spending and rapid urbanization is one of the major factors anticipated to drive the spring water market growth rate. Moreover, the rise in consumer awareness regarding the health benefits of consuming spring water is also expected to fuel the growth of the spring water market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Also the market is largely driven by the rise in consumer awareness regarding health benefits of preferring spring water. Additionally, the introduction of eco-friendly packaging and flavored water with regulated ingredients, easy portability and convenience provided by spring water along with the rapid expansion of restaurants are also expected to highly impact the growth of the spring water market. While, the high demand from huge population and inefficient water supply management in certain residential areas are also amongst the major factors expected to fuel the growth of the spring water market in the above mentioned forecast period.

In addition, the presence of large number of health-conscious consumers and increase in the incidences of diseases caused by the consumption of contaminated water are expected to bring various opportunities that will lead to the growth of the spring water market in the above mentioned forecast period.

However, the increase in environment pollution through plastic bottles and lack of awareness regarding health issues through low-cost tap water are expected to act as a major limiting factor for spring water market, whereas the, spring water is not cost effective when compared to the other drinks which can challenge the growth of the spring water market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

